after each sentence

*Smeš* se kad vidiš smešan film. (You laugh when you see a funny movie.)

Čovek se *smeši* kada je srećan. (The man smiles when he is happy.)

Ona je *smešna* devojka. (She is a funny girl.)

Ona je *smešila* sebi i njenim prijateljima. (She was making fun of herself and her friends.)

Ona je *smešio* sebi kosu. (She was styling her hair.)

On je *smeškao* sebi u ogledalo. (He was making faces at himself in the mirror.)